{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":23,"text":"[This talk contains graphic language\nand descriptions of sexual violence"},{"time":3488,"text":"Viewer discretion is advised]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":4893,"text":"Tom Stranger: In 1996,\nwhen I was 18 years old,"},{"time":7873,"text":"I had the golden opportunity to go\non an international exchange program."},{"time":12071,"text":"Ironically I'm an Australian\nwho prefers proper icy cold weather,"},{"time":15816,"text":"so I was both excited and tearful\nwhen I got on a plane to Iceland,"},{"time":20699,"text":"after just having farewelled\nmy parents and brothers goodbye."},{"time":24853,"text":"I was welcomed into the home\nof a beautiful Icelandic family"},{"time":27932,"text":"who took me hiking,"},{"time":29357,"text":"and helped me get a grasp\nof the melodic Icelandic language."},{"time":33213,"text":"I struggled a bit with the initial\nperiod of homesickness."},{"time":36225,"text":"I snowboarded after school,"},{"time":38247,"text":"and I slept a lot."},{"time":40480,"text":"Two hours of chemistry class in a language\nthat you don't yet fully understand"},{"time":44442,"text":"can be a pretty good sedative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46248,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48636,"text":"My teacher recommended\nI try out for the school play,"},{"time":51184,"text":"just to get me a bit more socially active."},{"time":54094,"text":"It turns out I didn't end up\nbeing part of the play,"},{"time":56619,"text":"but through it I met Thordis."},{"time":59451,"text":"We shared a lovely teenage romance,"},{"time":61538,"text":"and we'd meet at lunchtimes\nto just hold hands"},{"time":64056,"text":"and walk around old downtown Reykjavík."},{"time":66655,"text":"I met her welcoming family,\nand she met my friends."},{"time":70675,"text":"We'd been in a budding relationship\nfor a bit over a month"},{"time":73473,"text":"when our school's Christmas Ball was held."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78052,"text":"Thordis Elva: I was 16\nand in love for the first time."},{"time":81797,"text":"Going together to the Christmas dance"},{"time":83618,"text":"was a public confirmation\nof our relationship,"},{"time":86439,"text":"and I felt like the luckiest\ngirl in the world."},{"time":89430,"text":"No longer a child, but a young woman."},{"time":92730,"text":"High on my newfound maturity,"},{"time":94667,"text":"I felt it was only natural to try drinking\nrum for the first time that night, too."},{"time":99496,"text":"That was a bad idea."},{"time":101582,"text":"I became very ill,"},{"time":103094,"text":"drifting in and out of consciousness"},{"time":104938,"text":"in between spasms of convulsive vomiting."},{"time":108087,"text":"The security guards wanted\nto call me an ambulance,"},{"time":111075,"text":"but Tom acted as my knight\nin shining armor,"},{"time":114088,"text":"and told them he'd take me home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116782,"text":"It was like a fairy tale,"},{"time":118507,"text":"his strong arms around me,"},{"time":120307,"text":"laying me in the safety of my bed."},{"time":123602,"text":"But the gratitude that I felt\ntowards him soon turned to horror"},{"time":128153,"text":"as he proceeded to take off my clothes\nand get on top of me."},{"time":133457,"text":"My head had cleared up,"},{"time":134817,"text":"but my body was still\ntoo weak to fight back,"},{"time":137968,"text":"and the pain was blinding."},{"time":140765,"text":"I thought I'd be severed in two."},{"time":143804,"text":"In order to stay sane,"},{"time":145403,"text":"I silently counted the seconds\non my alarm clock."},{"time":149622,"text":"And ever since that night,"},{"time":151381,"text":"I've known that there are 7,200\nseconds in two hours."}]},{"cues":[{"time":159140,"text":"Despite limping for days\nand crying for weeks,"},{"time":162402,"text":"this incident didn't fit my ideas\nabout rape like I'd seen on TV."},{"time":167361,"text":"Tom wasn't an armed lunatic;"},{"time":169406,"text":"he was my boyfriend."},{"time":171193,"text":"And it didn't happen in a seedy alleyway,"},{"time":173826,"text":"it happened in my own bed."},{"time":176733,"text":"By the time I could identify\nwhat had happened to me as rape,"},{"time":180376,"text":"he had completed his exchange program"},{"time":182391,"text":"and left for Australia."},{"time":184532,"text":"So I told myself it was pointless\nto address what had happened."},{"time":188199,"text":"And besides,"},{"time":189408,"text":"it had to have been my fault, somehow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192685,"text":"I was raised in a world\nwhere girls are taught"},{"time":195014,"text":"that they get raped for a reason."},{"time":197784,"text":"Their skirt was too short,"},{"time":200373,"text":"their smile was too wide,"},{"time":202891,"text":"their breath smelled of alcohol."},{"time":206017,"text":"And I was guilty of all of those things,"},{"time":208807,"text":"so the shame had to be mine."},{"time":211675,"text":"It took me years to realize"},{"time":213123,"text":"that only one thing could have stopped me\nfrom being raped that night,"},{"time":217058,"text":"and it wasn't my skirt,"},{"time":219224,"text":"it wasn't my smile,"},{"time":221198,"text":"it wasn't my childish trust."},{"time":223832,"text":"The only thing that could've stopped me\nfrom being raped that night"},{"time":227590,"text":"is the man who raped me --"},{"time":229664,"text":"had he stopped himself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232729,"text":"TS: I have vague memories of the next day:"},{"time":235716,"text":"the after effects of drinking,"},{"time":238054,"text":"a certain hollowness\nthat I tried to stifle."},{"time":241631,"text":"Nothing more."},{"time":243745,"text":"But I didn't show up at Thordis's door."},{"time":247409,"text":"It is important to now state"},{"time":249239,"text":"that I didn't see my deed for what it was."},{"time":252658,"text":"The word \"rape\" didn't echo\naround my mind as it should've,"},{"time":256639,"text":"and I wasn't crucifying myself\nwith memories of the night before."},{"time":261524,"text":"It wasn't so much a conscious refusal,"},{"time":263922,"text":"it was more like any acknowledgment\nof reality was forbidden."},{"time":268365,"text":"My definition of my actions completely\nrefuted any recognition"},{"time":272503,"text":"of the immense trauma I caused Thordis."},{"time":276454,"text":"To be honest,"},{"time":277881,"text":"I repudiated the entire act\nin the days afterwards"},{"time":282758,"text":"and when I was committing it."},{"time":285443,"text":"I disavowed the truth by convincing\nmyself it was sex and not rape."},{"time":290788,"text":"And this is a lie I've felt\nspine-bending guilt for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296174,"text":"I broke up with Thordis\na couple of days later,"},{"time":298445,"text":"and then saw her a number of times"},{"time":300113,"text":"during the remainder\nof my year in Iceland,"},{"time":302195,"text":"feeling a sharp stab\nof heavyheartedness each time."},{"time":306314,"text":"Deep down, I knew I'd done\nsomething immeasurably wrong."},{"time":311326,"text":"But without planning it,\nI sunk the memories deep,"},{"time":314373,"text":"and then I tied a rock to them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318215,"text":"What followed is a nine-year period"},{"time":319985,"text":"that can best be titled\nas \"Denial and Running.\""},{"time":324010,"text":"When I got a chance to identify\nthe real torment that I caused,"},{"time":328513,"text":"I didn't stand still long enough to do so."},{"time":332102,"text":"Whether it be via distraction,"},{"time":334183,"text":"substance use,"},{"time":335683,"text":"thrill-seeking"},{"time":337325,"text":"or the scrupulous policing\nof my inner speak,"},{"time":340698,"text":"I refused to be static and silent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344927,"text":"And with this noise,"},{"time":346411,"text":"I also drew heavily\nupon other parts of my life"},{"time":349404,"text":"to construct a picture of who I was."},{"time":352636,"text":"I was a surfer,"},{"time":353890,"text":"a social science student,"},{"time":355631,"text":"a friend to good people,"},{"time":357741,"text":"a loved brother and son,"},{"time":360023,"text":"an outdoor recreation guide,"},{"time":361599,"text":"and eventually, a youth worker."},{"time":364119,"text":"I gripped tight to the simple notion\nthat I wasn't a bad person."},{"time":369460,"text":"I didn't think I had this in my bones."},{"time":372129,"text":"I thought I was made up of something else."},{"time":374608,"text":"In my nurtured upbringing,"},{"time":376192,"text":"my loving extended family and role models,"},{"time":379586,"text":"people close to me were warm and genuine"},{"time":381545,"text":"in their respect shown towards women."},{"time":384717,"text":"It took me a long time to stare down\nthis dark corner of myself,"},{"time":389567,"text":"and to ask it questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394231,"text":"TE: Nine years after the Christmas dance,"},{"time":396230,"text":"I was 25 years old,"},{"time":397735,"text":"and headed straight\nfor a nervous breakdown."},{"time":401098,"text":"My self-worth was buried\nunder a soul-crushing load of silence"},{"time":404746,"text":"that isolated me from everyone\nthat I cared about,"},{"time":408062,"text":"and I was consumed\nwith misplaced hatred and anger"},{"time":410991,"text":"that I took out on myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413635,"text":"One day, I stormed out\nof the door in tears"},{"time":416269,"text":"after a fight with a loved one,"},{"time":418236,"text":"and I wandered into a café,"},{"time":419959,"text":"where I asked the waitress for a pen."},{"time":422648,"text":"I always had a notebook with me,"},{"time":424518,"text":"claiming that it was to jot down ideas\nin moments of inspiration,"},{"time":428275,"text":"but the truth was that I needed\nto be constantly fidgeting,"},{"time":432529,"text":"because in moments of stillness,"},{"time":434440,"text":"I found myself counting seconds again."},{"time":438071,"text":"But that day, I watched in wonder\nas the words streamed out of my pen,"},{"time":443104,"text":"forming the most pivotal letter\nI've ever written,"},{"time":446189,"text":"addressed to Tom."},{"time":448295,"text":"Along with an account of the violence\nthat he subjected me to,"},{"time":451859,"text":"the words, \"I want to find forgiveness\""},{"time":455066,"text":"stared back at me,"},{"time":456574,"text":"surprising nobody more than myself."},{"time":459580,"text":"But deep down I realized that this\nwas my way out of my suffering,"},{"time":464290,"text":"because regardless of whether or not\nhe deserved my forgiveness,"},{"time":468351,"text":"I deserved peace."},{"time":471347,"text":"My era of shame was over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":476172,"text":"Before sending the letter,"},{"time":477695,"text":"I prepared myself for all kinds\nof negative responses,"},{"time":480466,"text":"or what I found likeliest:\nno response whatsoever."},{"time":485216,"text":"The only outcome\nthat I didn't prepare myself for"},{"time":487987,"text":"was the one that I then got --"},{"time":490240,"text":"a typed confession from Tom,\nfull of disarming regret."},{"time":495618,"text":"As it turns out, he, too,\nhad been imprisoned by silence."},{"time":500354,"text":"And this marked the start\nof an eight-year-long correspondence"},{"time":504428,"text":"that God knows was never easy,"},{"time":506876,"text":"but always honest."},{"time":509717,"text":"I relieved myself of the burdens\nthat I'd wrongfully shouldered,"},{"time":513328,"text":"and he, in turn, wholeheartedly\nowned up to what he'd done."},{"time":517415,"text":"Our written exchanges became a platform"},{"time":519711,"text":"to dissect the consequences of that night,"},{"time":522452,"text":"and they were everything\nfrom gut-wrenching"},{"time":524671,"text":"to healing beyond words."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527613,"text":"And yet, it didn't bring about\nclosure for me."},{"time":532358,"text":"Perhaps because the email format\ndidn't feel personal enough,"},{"time":535864,"text":"perhaps because it's easy to be brave"},{"time":537799,"text":"when you're hiding behind a computer\nscreen on the other side of the planet."},{"time":541931,"text":"But we'd begun a dialogue"},{"time":543741,"text":"that I felt was necessary\nto explore to its fullest."},{"time":548072,"text":"So, after eight years of writing,"},{"time":550161,"text":"and nearly 16 years after that dire night,"},{"time":553891,"text":"I mustered the courage\nto propose a wild idea:"},{"time":557746,"text":"that we'd meet up in person"},{"time":559430,"text":"and face our past once and for all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565171,"text":"TS: Iceland and Australia\nare geographically like this."},{"time":569250,"text":"In the middle of the two is South Africa."},{"time":572046,"text":"We decided upon the city of Cape Town,"},{"time":574975,"text":"and there we met for one week."},{"time":578426,"text":"The city itself proved to be\na stunningly powerful environment"},{"time":581920,"text":"to focus on reconciliation\nand forgiveness."},{"time":585847,"text":"Nowhere else has healing\nand rapprochement been tested"},{"time":588510,"text":"like it has in South Africa."},{"time":591036,"text":"As a nation, South Africa sought\nto sit within the truth of its past,"},{"time":594927,"text":"and to listen to the details\nof its history."},{"time":598819,"text":"Knowing this only magnified the effect\nthat Cape Town had on us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604006,"text":"Over the course of this week,"},{"time":605492,"text":"we literally spoke\nour life stories to each other,"},{"time":608406,"text":"from start to finish."},{"time":611305,"text":"And this was about analyzing\nour own history."},{"time":615568,"text":"We followed a strict policy\nof being honest,"},{"time":618425,"text":"and this also came\nwith a certain exposure,"},{"time":621374,"text":"an open-chested vulnerability."},{"time":624312,"text":"There were gutting confessions,"},{"time":626463,"text":"and moments where we just\nabsolutely couldn't fathom"},{"time":629311,"text":"the other person's experience."},{"time":632258,"text":"The seismic effects of sexual violence\nwere spoken aloud and felt,"},{"time":637176,"text":"face to face."},{"time":639979,"text":"At other times, though,"},{"time":641506,"text":"we found a soaring clarity,"},{"time":645164,"text":"and even some totally unexpected\nbut liberating laughter."},{"time":651250,"text":"When it came down to it,"},{"time":652804,"text":"we did out best to listen\nto each other intently."},{"time":657404,"text":"And our individual realities\nwere aired with an unfiltered purity"},{"time":663269,"text":"that couldn't do any less\nthan lighten the soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668508,"text":"TE: Wanting to take revenge\nis a very human emotion --"},{"time":672577,"text":"instinctual, even."},{"time":674829,"text":"And all I wanted to do for years"},{"time":676864,"text":"was to hurt Tom back as deeply\nas he had hurt me."},{"time":681658,"text":"But had I not found a way\nout of the hatred and anger,"},{"time":684735,"text":"I'm not sure I'd be standing here today."},{"time":688058,"text":"That isn't to say that I didn't have\nmy doubts along the way."},{"time":692689,"text":"When the plane bounced\non that landing strip in Cape Town,"},{"time":696374,"text":"I remember thinking,"},{"time":698001,"text":"\"Why did I not just get myself\na therapist and a bottle of vodka"},{"time":702231,"text":"like a normal person would do?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":704471,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":707415,"text":"At times, our search\nfor understanding in Cape Town"},{"time":710644,"text":"felt like an impossible quest,"},{"time":712835,"text":"and all I wanted to do was to give up"},{"time":714958,"text":"and go home to my loving\nhusband, Vidir,"},{"time":717198,"text":"and our son."},{"time":719994,"text":"But despite our difficulties,"},{"time":722381,"text":"this journey did result\nin a victorious feeling"},{"time":727033,"text":"that light had triumphed over darkness,"},{"time":730812,"text":"that something constructive\ncould be built out of the ruins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736572,"text":"I read somewhere"},{"time":737921,"text":"that you should try and be the person\nthat you needed when you were younger."},{"time":741806,"text":"And back when I was a teenager,"},{"time":743414,"text":"I would have needed to know\nthat the shame wasn't mine,"},{"time":747286,"text":"that there's hope after rape,"},{"time":749824,"text":"that you can even find happiness,"},{"time":751443,"text":"like I share with my husband today."},{"time":753861,"text":"Which is why I started writing feverishly\nupon my return from Cape Town,"},{"time":758240,"text":"resulting in a book co-authored by Tom,"},{"time":760988,"text":"that we hope can be of use\nto people from both ends"},{"time":764197,"text":"of the perpetrator-survivor scale."},{"time":767180,"text":"If nothing else,"},{"time":768658,"text":"it's a story that we would've needed\nto hear when we were younger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774726,"text":"Given the nature of our story,"},{"time":776571,"text":"I know the words\nthat inevitably accompany it --"},{"time":779933,"text":"victim, rapist --"},{"time":782513,"text":"and labels are a way to organize concepts,"},{"time":784792,"text":"but they can also be dehumanizing\nin their connotations."},{"time":789838,"text":"Once someone's been deemed a victim,"},{"time":791962,"text":"it's that much easier to file them away\nas someone damaged,"},{"time":797219,"text":"dishonored,"},{"time":798749,"text":"less than."},{"time":800643,"text":"And likewise, once someone\nhas been branded a rapist,"},{"time":803387,"text":"it's that much easier\nto call him a monster --"},{"time":806576,"text":"inhuman."},{"time":808614,"text":"But how will we understand\nwhat it is in human societies"},{"time":811669,"text":"that produces violence"},{"time":813274,"text":"if we refuse to recognize\nthe humanity of those who commit it?"},{"time":818534,"text":"And how --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":819722,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":821925,"text":"And how can we empower survivors\nif we're making them feel less than?"},{"time":828072,"text":"How can we discuss solutions\nto one of the biggest threats"},{"time":831523,"text":"to the lives of women and children\naround the world,"},{"time":834821,"text":"if the very words we use\nare part of the problem?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":841786,"text":"TS: From what I've now learnt,"},{"time":844302,"text":"my actions that night in 1996\nwere a self-centered taking."},{"time":850028,"text":"I felt deserving of Thordis's body."},{"time":853743,"text":"I've had primarily positive\nsocial influences"},{"time":856632,"text":"and examples of equitable\nbehavior around me."},{"time":859830,"text":"But on that occasion,"},{"time":861051,"text":"I chose to draw upon the negative ones."},{"time":863716,"text":"The ones that see women\nas having less intrinsic worth,"},{"time":867687,"text":"and of men having some unspoken\nand symbolic claim to their bodies."},{"time":873781,"text":"These influences I speak of\nare external to me, though."},{"time":877582,"text":"And it was only me in that room\nmaking choices,"},{"time":880387,"text":"nobody else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":882969,"text":"When you own something"},{"time":884778,"text":"and really square up to your culpability,"},{"time":888259,"text":"I do think a surprising thing can happen."},{"time":891249,"text":"It's what I call a paradox of ownership."},{"time":894989,"text":"I thought I'd buckle\nunder the weight of responsibility."},{"time":898377,"text":"I thought my certificate\nof humanity would be burnt."},{"time":902476,"text":"Instead, I was offered\nto really own what I did,"},{"time":907148,"text":"and found that it didn't possess\nthe entirety of who I am."},{"time":911460,"text":"Put simply,"},{"time":912845,"text":"something you've done doesn't have\nto constitute the sum of who you are."},{"time":918659,"text":"The noise in my head abated."},{"time":920951,"text":"The indulgent self-pity\nwas starved of oxygen,"},{"time":925003,"text":"and it was replaced\nwith the clean air of acceptance --"},{"time":930658,"text":"an acceptance that I did hurt\nthis wonderful person standing next to me;"},{"time":934966,"text":"an acceptance that I am part of a large\nand shockingly everyday grouping of men"},{"time":940589,"text":"who have been sexually violent\ntoward their partners."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944931,"text":"Don't underestimate the power of words."},{"time":948372,"text":"Saying to Thordis that I raped her\nchanged my accord with myself,"},{"time":953037,"text":"as well as with her."},{"time":955517,"text":"But most importantly,"},{"time":957013,"text":"the blame transferred from Thordis to me."},{"time":961331,"text":"Far too often,"},{"time":962506,"text":"the responsibility is attributed\nto female survivors of sexual violence,"},{"time":967114,"text":"and not to the males who enact it."},{"time":970736,"text":"Far too often,"},{"time":971910,"text":"the denial and running leaves all parties\nat a great distance from the truth."},{"time":978984,"text":"There's definitely a public\nconversation happening now,"},{"time":982371,"text":"and like a lot of people,"},{"time":984574,"text":"we're heartened\nthat there's less retreating"},{"time":987188,"text":"from this difficult\nbut important discussion."},{"time":991028,"text":"I feel a real responsibility\nto add our voices to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":998072,"text":"TE: What we did is not a formula\nthat we're prescribing for others."},{"time":1003182,"text":"Nobody has the right to tell anyone else\nhow to handle their deepest pain"},{"time":1008739,"text":"or their greatest error."},{"time":1011336,"text":"Breaking your silence is never easy,"},{"time":1013711,"text":"and depending on where\nyou are in the world,"},{"time":1015949,"text":"it can even be deadly\nto speak out about rape."},{"time":1020088,"text":"I realize that even the most\ntraumatic event of my life"},{"time":1024178,"text":"is still a testament to my privilege,"},{"time":1026961,"text":"because I can talk about it\nwithout getting ostracized,"},{"time":1030215,"text":"or even killed."},{"time":1032293,"text":"But with that privilege of having a voice"},{"time":1035246,"text":"comes the responsibility of using it."},{"time":1038733,"text":"That's the least I owe\nmy fellow survivors who can't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1044841,"text":"The story we've just relayed is unique,"},{"time":1047931,"text":"and yet it is so common with sexual\nviolence being a global pandemic."},{"time":1052621,"text":"But it doesn't have to be that way."},{"time":1055741,"text":"One of the things that I found useful\non my own healing journey"},{"time":1058781,"text":"is educating myself about sexual violence."},{"time":1061453,"text":"And as a result,\nI've been reading, writing"},{"time":1063891,"text":"and speaking about this issue\nfor over a decade now,"},{"time":1066568,"text":"going to conferences around the world."},{"time":1069144,"text":"And in my experience,"},{"time":1071147,"text":"the attendees of such events\nare almost exclusively women."},{"time":1077013,"text":"But it's about time that we stop treating\nsexual violence as a women's issue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1083653,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1097069,"text":"A majority of sexual violence\nagainst women and men"},{"time":1101137,"text":"is perpetrated by men."},{"time":1103044,"text":"And yet their voices are sorely\nunderrepresented in this discussion."},{"time":1108842,"text":"But all of us are needed here."},{"time":1113744,"text":"Just imagine all the suffering\nwe could alleviate"},{"time":1117653,"text":"if we dared to face this issue together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1122880,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1124062,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}